{"tid":945194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"ofo共享單車財困，用所已不能退押金，仲打算上市","createTime":"2018-12-17T16:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T06:11:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a48ec340e8664a63b693766403d41a0e22684da6","tid":945194,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:26:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>ofo無法在線退押 &ldquo;退押金&rdquo;按鈕成灰色無法點擊</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/fortune/2018-12/04/c_1123802700.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2Ffortune%2F2018-12%2F04%2Fc_1123802700.htm&d=a6qN6qdBUZo5aDlrCveKUsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=660e0af2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/fortune/2018-12/04/c_1123802700.htm</a><br />\n日前有消費者反映，ofo已經無法在App內退押金，&ldquo;退押金&rdquo;按鈕成灰色，無法點擊；餘額也無法在線退款；客服電話無法接通。ofo對媒體回應稱，目前退押金是正常的，不過該說法無法說服用戶，&ldquo;在線、電話都退不了押金，這哪裡正常了？&rdquo;還有大量用戶表示，ofo說的15個工作日根本無法兌現，自己一個月前申請的押金還未收到退款。<br />\n<br />\n　　北青報記者看到，目前在ofo的App內，最下方的&ldquo;退押金&rdquo;按鈕還存在，但成了灰色，無法點擊。&ldquo;到這裡就點不開那個退押金，ofo坑了我99元&rdquo;，來自太原的張女士對北青報記者表示，自己在ofo內的99元押金和15元餘額都不知道該怎麼辦，App內沒法退款。<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;我們現在退押金是正常的，正常的退押流程是在0到15個工作日，如果說有退款異常的情況，大家可以撥打我們的人工客服電話。現階段可能有時候會比較繁忙，撥打的人會比較多一點，所以說可能需要大家多打幾次。&rdquo;ofo負責人在回答央視記者採訪時表示。昨天，北青報記者多次嘗試撥打ofo客服電話，都提示&ldquo;對不起，您要的電話忙&rdquo;，就直接被掛斷。<br />\n<br />\n　　而ofo說好的15個退款工作日也無法實現。另一用戶王先生表示，自己10月底看到ofo的一些傳聞就趕緊選擇了退押金，但時至今日都未收到。&ldquo;說好的15個工作日根本無法兌現&rdquo;，王先生表示，目前系統一直顯示&ldquo;退款中&rdquo;，還讓用戶選擇將押金充值為餘額，&ldquo;押金充值餘額，即可享受免押金騎行&rdquo;。&ldquo;這太荒謬了，押金和餘額還能互相轉換？我的餘額還沒用完呢！&rdquo;王先生表示。與王先生有相同情況的用戶不在少數，目前ofo還沒有對此進行回應。"},{"pid":"b26a8f5f55a0f163829bc57de4f4a934d3e63eba","tid":945194,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T06:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f82d26aafd6609190c676176df8faacc575596","tid":945194,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"親，這是正常的"},{"pid":"a96cfc119af87fa55195ef61dcb965e2755cd246","tid":945194,"uid":90735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T06:16:14.000Z","msg":"新四大發明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6415fc6d435f3cbfbea5687d902ebba3b311a589","tid":945194,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T19:11:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TkK5HQrKHiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTkK5HQrKHiU&d=a6qN6qdBUZo5aDlrCveKUsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0ae44ac8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TkK5HQrKHiU</a>"},{"pid":"6144a51cf5a6b8f2424838a1623156d130c37042","tid":945194,"uid":187489,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T19:13:52.000Z","msg":"ofo死埋香港以後係咪會冇晒"},{"pid":"1c64caedb95da616d467f5bf7496bc1e584e2c3d","tid":945194,"uid":42536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T22:16:19.000Z","msg":"乜ofo背後唔係40大盜有份咩？咁大條水喉都要閂水？"},{"pid":"71deb82100bcc173ae1d550f008a1ea1e300301e","tid":945194,"uid":63909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1c64caedb95da616d467f5bf7496bc1e584e2c3d","tid":945194,"uid":42536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T22:16:19.000Z","msg":"乜ofo背後唔係40大盜有份咩？咁大條水喉都要閂水？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T22:36:36.000Z","msg":"話明大盜仲要成40個<br />\n呃錢就梗"},{"pid":"44ce50124ab81ff0832524bab216f9ba44ef3c08","tid":945194,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T00:57:14.000Z","msg":"成街免費單車"},{"pid":"cec9cd88254edb4911dcd112557613f86a841881","tid":945194,"uid":97340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T00:59:32.000Z","msg":"共享財困<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196f10a571d3ec496b224c546b99d46f1c59ffeb","tid